【教材】2014年韓永楷教授離散數學教材專區隆重登場囉！






回頂端








課程大綱

This course is about the study of discrete objects, and is one of the foundation courses in Computer Science. We will introduce a couple of basic concepts, and we hope that through the understanding of these concepts, we can strengthen our ability to understand a problem formulation, define a new problem, think critically...... 1.Course Description    This course is about the study of discrete objects, and is one of the foundation courses in Computer Science. We will introduce a couple of basic concepts, and we hope that through the understanding of these concepts, we can strengthen our ability to understand a problem formulation, define a new problem, think critically, and analyse the correctness and efficiency of a solution to a problem.   2.Text Book    Discrete Mathematics and Its Applications           by K. H. Rosen  3.References    A. ntroduction to Combinatorial Mathematics         by C. L. Liu   B. iscrete and Combinatorial Mathematics       by R. P. Grimaldi  4.Teaching Method       Lectures and Tutorials     (Lectures in English, Tutorial before Each Exam)  5.Syllabus     Here are the topics that I intend to cover:    A.Logic        (Propositional Logic, Predicate,Calculus,          Rules of Inference)    B.Proofs(Methods and Strategies, Math,Induction,                 Pigeonhole Principle)    C Counting(Basic, Permutation andCombination)    D.Sets, Functions, and Relations    E. Graphs(Introduction, Euler and Hamilton, Paths,                   Planar Graphs)    F.Trees(Introduction, Optimal Prefix Code,Minimu                Spanning Trees)  



回頂端








課程內容



第1講  Algorithm
第2講 Logical operators_review
第3講 Logical operators - L3_A Logical operators
第4講 Logic puzzles_Heaven or hell_1 people version
第5講 Predicate
第6講 Propositional function review
第7講 Valid argument forms
第8講 Axiom/Lemma/Corollary/Theorem/Conjecture
第9講 Indirect proofs
第10講 Pi mnemonic
第11講 Mathematical Induction
第12講 TA time&Strong Induction 
第13講 peg solitaire
第14講 Pigeonhole Principle
第15講 Pigeonhole Principle & Example
第16講 TA time
第17講 Counting
第18講 Combination & Permutation -L18_A Combination & Permutation
第19講 Example_star war VIII
第20講 Combinations & Permutations -L20_A Combinations & Permutations
第21講 Subset & Set Operations_Union, Intersection, Complement
第22講 Proving Set Identities
第23講 Q1-Q26研習題講解
第24講 Function(Injection/Surjection/Bijection)
第25講 Surjective Functions & Recurrence relation
第26講 Tutorial_exam2
第27講 Connected Component & Path
第28講 Planar Graphs
第29講 Subdivision & Platonic Solids
第30講 Tutorial









